<details>
  <summary>
    Group 3 Truck, Medium Procurement
  </summary>
  <hr />
  **Important Notes:**

  The procurement of nineteen (19) Medium Trucks and ancillary items has been announced. Due to the limited tendering reasons mentioned, this solicitation is restricted to suppliers holding a valid Supply Arrangement (SA) under the Request for Supply Arrangement (RFSA) E60HP-16TRUK Group X.

  **Contracting Authority:**

  * Organization: National Defence
  * Address: 101 Colonel by Drive, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A 0K2, Canada
  * Phone: (819) 939-3040
  * Email: victor.shepstone@forces.gc.ca

  **Solicitation Details:**

  * Solicitation Number: W8476-246762/A
  * Reference Number: cb-7929-6369503
  * Amendment Number: 6
  * Amendment Date: 2024-01-11
  * Tender Closing Date: 2024-01-11T14:00:00
  * Publication Date: 2023-11-02
  * Expected Contract Start Date: 2023-12-01
  * Expected Contract End Date: 2025-12-01

  **Request for a Proposal:**

  The Department of National Defence is seeking proposals for the supply of nineteen (19) Medium Trucks and ancillary items through the supply arrangement for Truck, Medium, Group 3, Configuration A, B, C. A pre-qualified supplier may obtain information on this proposal at: https://buyandsell.gc.ca/procurement-data/tender-notice/PW-HP-539-73419.

  **Delivery Terms:**

  The successful supplier must deliver the goods on or before 120 days after receiving the contract.

  **Security Requirements:**

  There are no security requirements associated with this solicitation.

  **Languages of Communications:**

  Documents may be submitted in either official language (English or French).

  **Trade Agreements:**

  This procurement falls under various trade agreements, including the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement, Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement, and the Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership.

  <hr />
  **Appendices:**

  No appendices are attached to this submission.
</details>
